article_id:567,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue in High Mercury's Trial [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where High Mercury sometimes performs an attack that cannot be dodged if you inflict the break status on High Mercury in a short amount of time after starting the quest.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently fixing this issue.</div><div>Any further updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1562824800"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>This issue was fixed in a data update applied <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1562824800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1562824800,update_time1562211289